Angel is the Sea 🌊
Started as an OC but got some hella Diluc hair so, Diluc it is? I really just wanted to draw a 4 winged mer cause 😍

Sorry long time no art but life is getting better and hopefully I can get back into doing art and stuff I like again soon :3 have a great week guys.

node.text:
If you would have told younger me I’d be drawing eren with a man bun in 2021 I’d have laughed.
